---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white border-b border-brand-border/40">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeader
      title="Built on Clarity, Process, and Practical Support"
      description="TheEduAssist works best when expectations are clear. Every project starts with an audit so we can understand your content, goals, platform needs, timeline, and scope before recommending the right service."
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

        <div class="bg-brand-softBg p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Clear Scope</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We define the structure and scope before we start building.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-softBg p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Human-Reviewed</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We use AI to assist, but all content is human-reviewed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-softBg p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Platform-Ready</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">Content is formatted and structured specifically for the platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-softBg p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Practical Support</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We focus on launch support, not fake promises or guaranteed sales claims.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
